ge` (for WirePayload validation), `blake3`, `thiserror`.\n\n## Tests\n\n- Round-trip: write N frames → read N frames, verify identical\n- Corrupt magic / checksum / truncated file → error\n- Empty bundle (0 frames) → valid\n- Large bundle (10k frames) → works\n- Fuzz harness for `BundleReader::open`\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- [ ] `cargo test -p reme-bundle` passes\n- [ ] Fuzz target added\n- [ ] No `unwrap()` in library code\n\n## Blocked by\n\nNothing — can start immediately.\n\n## Blocks\n\n- `reme export` CLI subcommand\n- `reme import` CLI subcommand\n- Migrate submit API to bundle format\n- Archive format spec document\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1",
