rm in `Cargo.toml` and `futures` (or `futures-lite`) as a dependency.\n\n## Source\n\nIdentified by ratatui ecosystem analysis (`docs/analysis/2026-03-27-ratatui-ecosystem-analysis.md`), Zero-Dependency Fix #2. Pattern used by twitch-tui.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- [ ] `event.rs` uses `EventStream` instead of `event::poll`\n- [ ] No blocking syscalls inside async context\n- [ ] All keyboard and resize events still work\n- [ ] `cargo test` and `cargo clippy` pass\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1",
