riteria\n\n- No blocking syscalls in async context\n- No wasted draws on idle ticks\n- Conversation list selection highlights and auto-scrolls correctly\n- No numeric `chunks[N]` index access in layout code\n- Popup rendering uses `tui-popup` widget\n- No `#[allow(clippy::too_many_lines)]` on `update()` or `handle_key_event()`\n- All async operations go through `BackendHandle`\n",
